1) create folder -demoapp any where in pc
2) make sure ypu have nodejs installed in your pc
3)go to demoapp folder via cmd --- command "npm install"
4)command-"npm install -g @angular/cli"
5)command-"ng new my-first-project
cd my-first-project
ng serve"
6)ng g c create 
7) replacce create-component.html and create-component.ts files with files from github repository.
8) now you can edit the create component
